thread.title: Nic

author: Nic
title: Nic
text: I took some convincing to use Ryan after I was leasing the property with a different agent. From that moment he made it so easy. Adriana and Ryan gave great advice throughout the campaign and kept me well informed with everything going on. Their summary before auction and their persistence with potential buyer got the people to the auction and a great result. Adriana and Ryan are very friendly and a great team. I would recommend them to anyone.
